<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>알림 | 서비스 에러</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* 순백색 배경 */
            font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, sans-serif;
            color: #1a1a1a; /* 짙은 회색 텍스트 */
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
            color: #f0f0f0; /* 배경과 대비되는 아주 연한 회색 */
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .message-box {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="error-code">ERROR</div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="message-box">
            <h1>문제가 발생했습니다.</h1>
            <p><%= typeof message !== 'undefined' ? message : '요청하신 페이지를 처리할 수 없습니다.' %></p>
            <a href="/list" class="back-link">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>